FastPattern.description: FailedAuthentication: Dynamic Authorization Failed for Device
FastPattern.matcher: (\d+)\s+([-\w.]+)\s+WARN:\s+(Dynamic Authorization Failed for Device)\s+:\s+Server=([-\w.]+); Network Device Name=([-\w.]+).*
FastPattern.pattern: WARN: Dynamic Authorization Failed for Device

FastFormatter.format: Auth Method: $8, Auth Identity Store: $9, Session ID: $10

FastPattern.matcher: (\d+)\s+([-\w.]+)\s+(CISE_Failed_Attempts) .+ NOTICE (?:RADIUS|Failed-Attempt): ([^,]+), ConfigVersionId=\d+, Device IP Address=([\d.]+),(?: Device Port=(\d+),)? DestinationIPAddress=([\d.]+),(?: DestinationPort=(\d+),.*? Protocol=(\w+),)?.*
FastPattern.pattern: CISE_Failed_Attempts \d+ \d+ \d+ .* NOTICE (?:RADIUS|Failed-Attempt): (?:NAS conducted several failed authentications of the same scenario|DACL Download Failed|Endpoint conducted several failed|Endpoint abandoned EAP session and started new)
CISE_Alarm WARN: No (?:ISE Authentications|Accounting messages) in the last
CISE_Alarm WARN: (?:No ISE configuration backup has been scheduled|\S+ \>\> \w+ License expires)

FastPattern.matcher: (\d+)\s+([-\w.]+)\s+(CISE_Passed_Authentications) .+ NOTICE Passed-Authentication: ([^,]+), ConfigVersionId=\d+, Device IP Address=([\d.]+), DestinationIPAddress=([\d.]+), DestinationPort=(\d+), UserName=(\S+), Protocol=(\w+),.*

(\d+)\s+([-\w.]+)\s+(CISE_Administrative_and_Operational_Audit) .+ NOTICE \S+: ([^,]+), ConfigVersionId=\d+,(?: AdminInterface=([^,]+),)? AdminIPAddress=([\d.]+),.*?(?: AdminName=([^,]+),)? OperationMessageText=([^,]+),.*
(\d+)\s+([-\w.]+)\s+(CISE_Failed_Attempts) .+ NOTICE RADIUS: ([^,]+), ConfigVersionId=\d+, NAS-IP-Address=([\d.]+),.*? Calling-Station-ID=([^,]+), Acct-Status-Type=([^,]+), FailureReason=\d+.*
FastPattern.pattern: CISE_Failed_Attempts \d+ \d+ \d+ .* NOTICE RADIUS: RADIUS packet already in the process,

FastPattern.description: ServiceWarning WARN RAIDUS Authentication Request Dropped
FastPattern.matcher: (\d+) ([-\w.]+) WARN: ([^:]+): Server=([^;]+); NAS IP Address=([\d.]+); NAS Identifier=[^;]+; Failure Reason=\d+ (.*)
